    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 的收益将考验标准普尔 500 指数 4 万亿美元的复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/nvidia-s-earnings-will-test-the-s-p-500-s-4-trillion-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 ChatGPT 推出以来的大约两年时间里，英伟达公司股价上涨了近 3 万亿美元，几乎改变了美国股市，使这家人工智能芯片制造巨头对一系列股票指数产生了巨大影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/nvidia-s-earnings-will-test-the-s-p-500-s-4-trillion-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率投机推动美元上涨，新兴资产小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元从上周末触及的近八个月低点反弹，新兴市场货币周三小幅下跌，而股票交易员则等待当天晚些时候英伟达公司 (Nvidia Inc.) 的业绩线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
